xl-fortran. for questions about using the ibm xl fortran compiler.  see also the fortran tag for questions about the fortran language itself.
postgresql parallel query. parallel query in postgresql enables multiple threads working on the same table for the same query in parallel.
having-clause. about the having keyword in sql.
elasticsearch-plugin. elasticsearch plugins are a way to enhance the basic elasticsearch functionality in a custom manner.
nuxt3. please use the nuxtjs3 tag for nuxt3 related questions.

thredds. thredds is an acronym for thematic realtime environmental distributed data services. the goal of the project is developing middleware to bridge the gap between data providers and data users. the goal is to simplify the discovery and use of scientific data and to allow scientific publications and educational materials to reference scientific data.

vscode-tasks. visual studio code tasks can be used to run scripts or begin processes in order to leverage other tools to perform tasks from within visual studio code.
type-assertion. a type assertion is like a type cast, but performs no special checking or restructuring of data. it has no runtime impact, and is used purely by the compiler for type checking.
pyfilesystem. questions related to the pyfilesystem python library, which is a standardized file system on top of many other types of filesystem (os, temp, aws s3, etc.).
uber-kraken. kraken is a p2p-powered docker registry that focuses on scalability and availability.

staticlayout. an android text layout class for laying out text that will not change.

inputmethodmanager. the inputmethodmanager is an android api for interacting with input methods (keyboards, etc.)
apache sentry. apache sentry is a system for enforcing fine grained role based authorization to data and metadata stored on a hadoop cluster.

secure copy. for questions around "secure copy protocol" (scp). general scp support is off-topic. support questions may be asked on https://superuser.com. secure copy protocol or scp is a means of securely transferring computer files between a local and a remote host or between two remote hosts over an ssh protocol. this tag is not related to "sap cloud platform"!
xbehave.net. use this tag for questions relating to xbehave.net, the extension for xunit.net for describing your tests using natural language.
django 1.2. django 1.2 is a version of the django framework, released in may 2010. please only use this tag if your question relates specifically to this version.
polyphonic-c#. polyphonic c# is a research extension to c# which contains asynchronous concurrency abstractions, intended for both multithreaded and asynchronous event-driven programs.

vfork. vfork() is a c function available on many unix-like systems to fork a process.  there are strict rules about what you can do in the child process.  it was part of posix (single unix specification) in the 1997 and 2004 editions (marked 'obsolescent' in posix 2004), but it is not a part of posix 2008 (2016).
qframe. qframe is a class from the qt toolkit which provides the base class for widgets that can have a frame.

pebble-sdk. the pebble sdk is a software development kit for the pebble smartwatch and the pebble app store. it is generally installed on a computer and includes all of the libraries available to developers for pebble.
cloudpebble. cloudpebble was a website that provides a toolkit for developing apps using c and javascript for the pebble smartwatch through an online ide.
reactivecocoa. reactivecocoa (rac) is a swift framework inspired by functional reactive programming. it provides apis for composing and transforming streams of values.
theme-daynight. questions related to daynight theme, that changes colors according to time of the day and battery status.

rtk. real time kinematic
is a satellite navigation technique used to enhance the precision of position data derived from satellite-based positioning systems (global navigation satellite systems, gnss) such as gps, beidou, glonass, galileo, etc

haskell platform. the haskell platform is a standardized multi-os distribution for the haskell programming language. questions on this tag should not be about the haskell language in general, but specific to issues with the platform installer and distribution.
getid3. getid3 is an open source php library that extracts useful information from mp3s and other multimedia file formats
swarmplot. a swarm plot (also known as a "beeswarm plot") is a type of data visualization that presents a categorical scatterplot with non-overlapping points.
madbee. madbee or managed-adb is a library to access adb in managed environment such as c#

clickdimensions. clickdimensions is a marketing automation solution for the microsoft dynamics marketplace built on the microsoft azure cloud computing platform.
